javax.swing.text.html.parser
Interface DTDConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
AttributeList, DTD, Element, Entity, Parser, TagStack
public interface DTDConstants

Untamed: SGML constants used in a DTD. The names of the constants correspond the the equivalent SGML constructs as described in "The SGML Handbook" by Charles F. Goldfarb.

Version:
1.8, 12/03/01
Author:
Arthur van Hoff
See Also:
DTD, Element
